tafsir[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan mofte maa ﾉ容n: Allah wahayinii e am, wonnde dental jinna heﾉ擁tike lam Ba盪ｭnu Nakhlah, miﾉ熔 jannga Alqur'aanaa. Nde ﾉ擁 ruttinoo ka jamaa majji, ﾉ擁 wi'ani ﾉ擁n : Menen men nani konngol hino janngee, haawniingol e ﾉ殿nnginol e laaﾉ砥gol mun."
  72,2,"Ngol konngol ngol men nani, hino fewnira e peewal ka fiﾉ渡de, e ka konngol e ka kuugal. Men gomﾉ擁nii nde. Men kafidataa e Joomi amen jippinﾉ熔 nde On, hay e gooto."
  72,3,"Men gomﾉ擁nirii Mo, tawde manngural Joomi amen ngal toowii, O siforaali jogitagol ﾉ兎yngu, wanaa ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔."
  72,4,"E wonnde Ibuliisa hino wowlaynoo peenale e hoore Allah, ﾉ兎 dammba genndo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 e Makko."
  72,5,"Menen men sikkuo wonnde sirkooﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 e jinna ﾉ兎n wonah fenaande wowlunoo, fewndo ﾉ兎 aaﾆｴinoo wonnde Allah no jogitii genndo e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔. Men goongini ﾉ兎 men jokki ﾉ兎."
  72,6,"Hari ado islaamu, worﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 goo hino mooloraynoo worﾉ兎 jinna goo, tuma kala ﾉ兎 hewti e nokku hulﾉ妬niiﾉ熔, nanaa hiﾉ兎 wi'a: mi moolorii koohoojo ndee aynde, immorde e bone ﾉ預ytuﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 mun ﾉ兎n. Worﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎ydii hulugol ﾉ容ﾆｴnoo worﾉ兎 jinna ﾉ兎n."
  72,7,"Yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n sikkir no sikkirﾉ熔n non onon jinnaaji ﾉ擁n, wonnde Allah immintintaa hay gooto fii ﾃｱaaweede yoﾉ妬tee, ﾉ殿awo maayde mun."
  72,8,"Men tefuno fii kammu ngun, men tawi hingu hebbiniraa Malaa'ka aynooﾉ兎 tiiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎, ko ayna ko men heﾉ擁totonoo kon. Ngu hebbiniraa kadi yiite ko fiﾉ擁ree kala ﾉ殿diiﾉ熔 ngu."
  72,9,"Hari meﾉ容n jooﾉ熔tonoo ka kammu ton fii heﾉ預gol ko Malaa'ika'en wowlata, men heﾉ殿 ko men humpita ndureeﾉ兎 leydi ndin, kono ﾉ蓉m wayiima. Kala heﾉ擁tiiﾉ熔 e amen jooni, o hawray e docotal yiite, no o ﾉ殿dori, ngal sunna mo."
  72,10,"E wonnde men anndaa sabu ngol aygnugol kammu ngun. Hara ko bone faandoraa yimﾉ兎 leydi ndin? Kaa hara Allah faandani ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴere. Kumpite kammu ngun majjitorike men."
  72,11,"E wonnde menen jinnaaji ﾉ擁n, hino e amen gomﾉ蓉ﾉ擁 ﾉ擁gguﾉ擁, hino e amen kadi keeferi naafiqiiji. Hari ko men nooneeji seertuﾉ擁."
  72,12,"E wonnde men yanano men laawotaako Allah seniiﾉ熔 On, si O faandanike men huunde, ko non kadi men laawortaa Mo dogugol, tawde Himo huﾉ妬ndii men."
  72,13,"E wonnde nde men nanunoo Alqur'aana fewnaynde nden, men gomﾉ擁nno nde. Kala gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 Joomi mun, on hulataa ﾉ蓉ytaneede moﾆｴﾆｴi mun, maa ﾉ兎ydaneede bonﾉ擁 goo e hoore adinooﾉ擁."
  72,14,"E wonnde hino e amen julﾉ蓉ﾉ擁 jebbiliranii Allah ﾉ熔ftagol Mo, hino e amen kadi ooﾃｱiiﾉ擁 seli goonga e ﾃｱiiﾉ殿l. Kala non jebbiliranii ngii Allah ﾉ熔ftagol golla ko moﾆｴﾆｴi, ko ﾉ擁n woni faandiiﾉ擁 peewal e sawaaba."
  72,15,"Ooﾃｱiiﾉ擁 e laawol goonga e ﾃｱiiﾉ殿l ﾉ擁n kan, ﾉ擁 laatanike Jahannama on carmalle huﾉ橡妬nirﾉ容 nge, kannji e yimﾉ兎 nannduﾉ兎 e majji."
  72,16,"Ko wano wahayiniraa non e makko fii dental jinna heﾉ擁nooﾉ擁 Alqur'aana ﾉ擁n, ko non kadi wahayiniraa e makko wonnde si jinna e yimﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ砥no e laawol Islaamu ngol, ﾉ兎 gollitiri ko woni e mun kon, ko pellet, Allah yeﾉ預yno ﾉ兎 ndiyam ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ預m, O neeminira ﾉ兎 kadi ko seertuﾉ擁."
  72,17,"Fii no Men ndaarndora ﾉ兎 ﾉ預m si ﾉ兎 yettay neema Allah on kaa hara ﾉ兎 yedday mo? Kala ﾉ蓉urniiﾉ熔 Alqur'aana e waajuuji ko woni kon e mayre, Joomi makko naadoyay mo e lette sattuﾉ容 ﾉ容 o townoytaa."
  72,18,"E wonnde juulirﾉ容 ﾉ容n ko Allah tun heeranii. Wata on rewidu e Allah ton hay e gooto, haa wa'on wa Alyahuuda e Annasaara'en ka cuuﾉ擁 dewe maﾉ橡兎."
  72,19,"E wonnde tuma Muhammadu jeyaaﾉ熔 Allah (yo o his) darinoo himo rewa Joomi makko ka wi'etee : ""Ba盪ｭnu Nakhlah"", jinnaaji ﾉ擁n eﾉ橡砥no fawondirgol e hoore makko, hakkee ﾉ妬ﾆｴondiro fii heﾉ預gol himo jannga Alqur'aana."
  72,20,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 : Anndee ko Joomi am tun min mi rewata, mi kafidataa Mo e goﾉ遼蓉m goo no wa'i woo."
  72,21,"Maakan ﾉ兎 : min on mi waawanaa on duﾃｱogol lorra mo Allah hoddirani on, wanaa fii pooﾉ蓉gol nafa mo Allah ﾉ預wi on."
  72,22,"Maakan ﾉ兎 : Hay gooto waawaa daﾉ溶dude lam e Allah si mi yeddii Mo; mi heﾉ殿taa kadi ko woori Mo ﾆｴooﾃｱorde ka mi moolotoo."
  72,23,"Ko mi waawani on, ko yottingol ko Allah nulin mi kon e mon, e nule Makko ﾉ容 O imminirimmi ﾉ容n e mon. Kala yedduﾉ熔 Allah e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on, hara depporde makko nden ko ka Yiite Jahannama, o lutta e magge, o yaltataa poomaa."
  72,24,"Heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n heddoray non e yeddugol haa si ﾉ兎 yi'oyii lette ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 kammbirananoo ﾉ容n aduna, ontuma ﾉ兎 anndoyto ko hombo ﾉ砥ri lo'ude ballo, ﾉ砥ri kadi fanﾉ蓉de wallooﾉ兎."
  72,25,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 fii ummital : mi anndaa si tawii lette ﾉ容 kammbiranaﾉ熔n ﾉ容n hino ﾉ殿dii, maa si tawii ﾉ容 happanaa lajal ngal Allah tun anndii fii mun."
  72,26,"Kanko seniiﾉ熔 On ko O annduﾉ熔 wirniiﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n fow. Huunde e ﾉ蓉m wirnanaaki Mo. O ﾆｴellintinantaa wirniiﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n e hay e gooto. Ko Kanko tun heertorii ko O anndi fii mun kon."
  72,27,"Si wanaa mo Allah suﾉ妬i e Nulaaﾉ熔, O ﾆｴellintinay on ﾉ熔n ko O muuyi woo, O immina Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 reenooﾉ兎 yeeso on Nulaaﾉ熔 ko ayna mo, fii wata mo wanaa Nulaaﾉ熔 ﾆｴellito e ﾉ蓉m."
  72,28,"Fii yo Nulaaﾉ熔 on anndu wonnde imminaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko adii mbo ﾉ兎 yottinii Nule Joomi mun ﾉ擁n, tawde Allah no huﾉ妬ndori ko woni ka Malaa'ika e Nulaaﾉ兎 fow e mun ganndal. Huunde wirnaaki Mo fii maﾉ橡兎. Himo mofti limoore kala huunde. Hay huunde suuﾉ預aki Seniiﾉ熔 On."
